                            Admissions Criteria
PMRE welcomes applications from well-rounded individuals with minimum 2 years’ work experience who bring unique insight to the classroom learning environment and team experience.
Follow these steps to apply:
1.	Complete the online application and remit the $30 application fee.
2.	Submit all required documents, including transcripts, GMAT or GRE test scores, letters of recommendation, and essay.
3.	Schedule an interview with the PMRE Admissions Committee.
