                Tuition Schedule
The tuition for the PMRE program is an all-inclusive package. It covers all tuition costs, textbooks, laptop computer, orientation, parking during class times, class shirt, lifetime membership to the UCF Alumni Association, and all administrative fees. This fee applies to Florida residents only. Non-Florida residents should contact the Executive Development Center to determine the current out-of-state tuition rate for the PMBA program.
Many employers offer PMRE reimbursement packages. Please check with your employer to determine the availability of financial assistance.
Participants of the PMRE program are often eligible for financial aid. Contact UCF’s Financial Aid department for more information.

